<%- include("../header.ejs", {
    pageTitle: "Give",
    pageDescription: "Support the Crafting for Christ network"
}) %>

<%- include("../navigationBar.ejs") %>

<style>
    .hero-section {
        background: url('<%= globalImage %>') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 100px 0;
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    .section-light {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .section-dark {
        background-color: #e9ecef;
    }
    .card-icon {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
</style>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="hero-section text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4">🙏 Support the Crafting For Christ Network</h1>
        <p class="lead">Crafting For Christ exists to provide a safe, encouraging, Christ-centred community for players around the world. Your generosity helps keep the network running, growing, and reaching more people every day.</p>
        <a href="/ranks" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">View Ranks & Perks</a>
        <a href="<%= config.siteConfiguration.platforms.webstore %>" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Give a Gift or Rank</a>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Why We Give Section -->
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h2 class="mb-4">✨ Why Support the Network?</h2>
                <p>Crafting For Christ is fully community-funded. Your support directly helps us continue providing:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-server card-icon text-primary"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text text-center">Reliable and high-performance Minecraft servers</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt card-icon text-success"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text text-center">A safe, wholesome place to play and grow</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt card-icon text-info"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text text-center">Resources for events, ministry projects, and outreach</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-users card-icon text-warning"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text text-center">An environment where friendships and faith flourish</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Monthly Operations Goal Section -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-4">💰 Monthly Operations Budget</h2>
                <p>Each month, we trust God to provide what’s needed to keep the network running. Below is our current month’s support progress:</p>
                <div class="progress" style="height: 30px;">
                    <div id="progress-bar" class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 0%;" aria-valuenow="0" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-3"><span id="progress-text"></span></p>
                <p><small>Every purchase or donation made through our store contributes directly to this goal.</small></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Ways to Support Section -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-4">💬 How You Can Support</h2>
                <p>There are two main ways you can help sustain the ministry:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">1. Purchasing a Rank</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">Rank purchases help fund operations and come with fun perks and cosmetics.</p>
                        <a href="/ranks" class="btn btn-primary">Explore ranks and perks</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">2. Monthly Support Tiers</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">Recurring support is the most impactful way to help us meet our monthly operations budget.</p>
                        <a href="<%= config.siteConfiguration.platforms.webstore %>" class="btn btn-secondary">Visit the webstore to subscribe or give</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 text-center mt-3">
                <p>You can also gift a rank to bless another player!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Heart & Mission Reminder Section -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-4">❤️ Why Your Support Matters</h2>
                <p>Your contributions make a real difference. Because of your support, players from all over the world are finding a community where they can:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success"></i> Meet positive, Christ-following friends</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success"></i> Find prayer, encouragement, and support</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success"></i> Participate in events, worship nights, and community projects</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <p>Crafting For Christ is more than a server — it’s a ministry. You’re helping keep that ministry alive.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Thank You Section -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-4">🙏 Thank You</h2>
                <p>Thank you for praying for our team, supporting the network, and being part of our community. Your generosity helps us continue doing what God has called us to do.</p>
                <p class="lead">“And whatever you do, whether in word or deed, do it all in the name of the Lord Jesus…” — Colossians 3:17</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
    fetch("/api/give/goal")
      .then(response => response.json())
      .then(data => {
        if (data.success) {
          const progressBar = document.getElementById("progress-bar");
          const progressText = document.getElementById("progress-text");

          progressBar.style.width = data.percentage + "%";
          progressBar.setAttribute("aria-valuenow", data.percentage);
          progressBar.innerText = data.percentage + "% Funded";
          progressText.innerText = "$" + data.current + " raised of $" + data.goal + " goal";
        }
      });
  });
</script>

<%- include("../footer.ejs") %>
